      <title>泰坦尼克号船厂所有者将于本周进入破产程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/titanic-shipyard-owner-harland-wolff-ready-to-enter-administration-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[建造泰坦尼克号的造船厂的所有者正在进入破产程序，这是五年内第二次进入破产程序。]]></description>
